==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Solvable
<hw>Solv"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>solvable</ets>. See <er>Solve</er>, and cf. <er>Soluble</er>,
<er>Solvible</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Susceptible of being solved,
resolved, or explained; admitting of solution.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Capable of being paid and discharged; <as>as,
<ex>solvable</ex> obligations</as>.</def> <rj><au>Tooke.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Able to pay one's debts; solvent.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Fuller.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Solvableness</ent>⟦br⟧
